problems.description: A candidate qualifies only if written score is at least 60 interview score at least 15 and total does not exceed 100.
Determine whether two numeric ranges overlap.
A container must hold between 200 and 500 units. Find the first value that violates this.
Check whether three sides can form a valid triangle.
Admission is granted only if math is at least 70 science is at least 65 and average is at least 75.
